<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="378" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,527,1165,1228]" box="[151,217,1202,1228]" pageId="3" pageNumber="378">
<figureCitation box="[151,217,1202,1228]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="5.[151,248,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[195,1394,212,1920]" captionTargetId="figure-19@5.[179,1408,181,1920]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 3. I. serratastylus sp. nov. A, adult, dorsal view; B, face; C, adult, lateral view; D, Pygofer and subgential plate, lateral view; E, valve; F, connective, dorsal view; G, style, dorsal view; H, aedeagus, ventral view; I, aedeagus, lateral view." pageId="3" pageNumber="378">Fig. 3</figureCitation>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,1273,2032]" box="[151,1379,1273,1301]" pageId="3" pageNumber="378">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,297,1273,1299]" pageId="3" pageNumber="378">Description.</emphasis>
Small-sized species. Body length (including forewing): male, 
<quantity box="[998,1135,1274,1300]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.15" metricValueMax="4.2" metricValueMin="4.1" pageId="3" pageNumber="378" unit="mm" value="4.15" valueMax="4.2" valueMin="4.1">4.1–4.2 mm</quantity>
, female, 
<quantity box="[1237,1375,1274,1300]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.25" metricValueMax="4.4" metricValueMin="4.1" pageId="3" pageNumber="378" unit="mm" value="4.25" valueMax="4.4" valueMin="4.1">4.1–4.4 mm</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,1273,2032]" pageId="3" pageNumber="378">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,335,1308,1334]" pageId="3" pageNumber="378">Coloration.</emphasis>
General color (
<figureCitation box="[509,629,1308,1335]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="5.[151,248,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[195,1394,212,1920]" captionTargetId="figure-19@5.[179,1408,181,1920]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 3. I. serratastylus sp. nov. A, adult, dorsal view; B, face; C, adult, lateral view; D, Pygofer and subgential plate, lateral view; E, valve; F, connective, dorsal view; G, style, dorsal view; H, aedeagus, ventral view; I, aedeagus, lateral view." pageId="3" pageNumber="378">Fig. 3A–C</figureCitation>
) ochraceous. Crown and pronotum yellowish, eyes dark brown to black. Pronotum posterior margin with ochraceous broad band. Forewings (
<figureCitation box="[943,1068,1343,1369]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="5.[151,248,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[195,1394,212,1920]" captionTargetId="figure-19@5.[179,1408,181,1920]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 3. I. serratastylus sp. nov. A, adult, dorsal view; B, face; C, adult, lateral view; D, Pygofer and subgential plate, lateral view; E, valve; F, connective, dorsal view; G, style, dorsal view; H, aedeagus, ventral view; I, aedeagus, lateral view." pageId="3" pageNumber="378">Fig. 3A, C</figureCitation>
) with two yellowish patches on clavus, black apically. Legs (
<figureCitation box="[475,560,1378,1404]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="5.[151,248,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[195,1394,212,1920]" captionTargetId="figure-19@5.[179,1408,181,1920]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 3. I. serratastylus sp. nov. A, adult, dorsal view; B, face; C, adult, lateral view; D, Pygofer and subgential plate, lateral view; E, valve; F, connective, dorsal view; G, style, dorsal view; H, aedeagus, ventral view; I, aedeagus, lateral view." pageId="3" pageNumber="378">Fig. 3C</figureCitation>
) green.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,1273,2032]" box="[199,947,1412,1438]" pageId="3" pageNumber="378">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,381,1412,1438]" pageId="3" pageNumber="378">Wing venation.</emphasis>
Forewing with only middle anteapical cell closed.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,1273,2032]" pageId="3" pageNumber="378">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,380,1447,1473]" pageId="3" pageNumber="378">Male genitalia.</emphasis>
Pygofer (
<figureCitation box="[498,589,1447,1473]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="5.[151,248,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[195,1394,212,1920]" captionTargetId="figure-19@5.[179,1408,181,1920]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 3. I. serratastylus sp. nov. A, adult, dorsal view; B, face; C, adult, lateral view; D, Pygofer and subgential plate, lateral view; E, valve; F, connective, dorsal view; G, style, dorsal view; H, aedeagus, ventral view; I, aedeagus, lateral view." pageId="3" pageNumber="378">Fig. 3D</figureCitation>
) ventral margin slightly concave. Male valve (
<figureCitation box="[1136,1224,1447,1473]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="5.[151,248,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[195,1394,212,1920]" captionTargetId="figure-19@5.[179,1408,181,1920]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 3. I. serratastylus sp. nov. A, adult, dorsal view; B, face; C, adult, lateral view; D, Pygofer and subgential plate, lateral view; E, valve; F, connective, dorsal view; G, style, dorsal view; H, aedeagus, ventral view; I, aedeagus, lateral view." pageId="3" pageNumber="378">Fig. 3E</figureCitation>
) basal margin not curved, apex convex medially, with notched median projection. Subgenital plate (
<figureCitation box="[1053,1139,1482,1508]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="5.[151,248,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[195,1394,212,1920]" captionTargetId="figure-19@5.[179,1408,181,1920]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 3. I. serratastylus sp. nov. A, adult, dorsal view; B, face; C, adult, lateral view; D, Pygofer and subgential plate, lateral view; E, valve; F, connective, dorsal view; G, style, dorsal view; H, aedeagus, ventral view; I, aedeagus, lateral view." pageId="3" pageNumber="378">Fig. 3D</figureCitation>
) bent dorsad at right-angle near midlength. Connective (
<figureCitation box="[479,563,1516,1543]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="5.[151,248,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[195,1394,212,1920]" captionTargetId="figure-19@5.[179,1408,181,1920]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 3. I. serratastylus sp. nov. A, adult, dorsal view; B, face; C, adult, lateral view; D, Pygofer and subgential plate, lateral view; E, valve; F, connective, dorsal view; G, style, dorsal view; H, aedeagus, ventral view; I, aedeagus, lateral view." pageId="3" pageNumber="378">Fig. 3F</figureCitation>
) wide and short. Style (
<figureCitation box="[834,922,1516,1543]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="5.[151,248,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[195,1394,212,1920]" captionTargetId="figure-19@5.[179,1408,181,1920]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 3. I. serratastylus sp. nov. A, adult, dorsal view; B, face; C, adult, lateral view; D, Pygofer and subgential plate, lateral view; E, valve; F, connective, dorsal view; G, style, dorsal view; H, aedeagus, ventral view; I, aedeagus, lateral view." pageId="3" pageNumber="378">Fig. 3G</figureCitation>
) slightly bent, base expanded, medial margin serrated subapically. Aedeagal shaft (
<figureCitation box="[569,680,1551,1578]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="5.[151,248,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[195,1394,212,1920]" captionTargetId="figure-19@5.[179,1408,181,1920]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 3. I. serratastylus sp. nov. A, adult, dorsal view; B, face; C, adult, lateral view; D, Pygofer and subgential plate, lateral view; E, valve; F, connective, dorsal view; G, style, dorsal view; H, aedeagus, ventral view; I, aedeagus, lateral view." pageId="3" pageNumber="378">Fig. 3H, I</figureCitation>
) cylindrical, uniform from base to subapex, with pair of long, thin, curved subapical processes, apex flat and slightly broadened in posterior view.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,1273,2032]" pageId="3" pageNumber="378">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,453,1620,1647]" pageId="3" pageNumber="378">Measurements (mm).</emphasis>
Male: body length 4.10–4.20, face length 1.20–1.30, width 1.30–1.40; distance between ocelli 0.20–0.30; distance from ocellus to eyes 0.30–0.40; medial length of pronotum 0.35–0.40, width 0.68–0.72; scutellum length 0.80–0.90, width 0.53–0.56.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
